sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Colab as Colab Notebook
    participant Rclone as Rclone Daemon
    participant Drive as Google Drive
    participant Network as Torrent Network

    User->>Colab: Run Setup
    Colab->>Colab: Install Tools
    
    User->>Colab: Run Mount
    Colab->>User: Prompt for Rclone Config
    User->>Colab: Paste Config/Auth Code
    Colab->>Rclone: Start Daemon (VFS Mode)
    Rclone->>Drive: Mount /content/drive_rclone
    
    User->>Colab: Run Download
    Colab->>User: Prompt Magnet
    User->>Colab: Paste Magnet
    
    Colab->>Drive: Check for .fastresume
    alt Resume Data Found
        Drive-->>Colab: Return Data
        Colab->>Network: Start (No Re-check)
    else New Download
        Colab->>Network: Start Normal
    end
    
    loop Downloading
        Colab->>Rclone: Write Data
        Rclone->>Drive: Upload (Background)
        Colab->>Drive: Save .fastresume (Every 60s)
    end
    
    User->>Colab: Click Stop
    Colab->>Drive: Save Final .fastresume
    Colab->>User: "Saved. Safe to close."
